    {
      "note": "Summary of Original Version",
      "abstract": "Amend KRS 610.200 to define \"custodial interrogation\"; require a peace officer to arrange for a child to consult with legal counsel prior to any interview or custodial interrogation; amend KRS 610.220 and 630.040 to conform; make technical corrections."
